DataElement.preferredName: None Image Quantification Person Observer Statistical Confidence ISO21090.REAL.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: No person or thing, nobody, not any.:The process of measuring attributes of an image, by human sense or machine observations and experiences, and mapping them into members of some set of numbers or coded concepts._Human observer created the observations.:The statistical calculation of the percentage likelihood for a given set of data to have a given statistical value._Fractional numbers represented by decimals.
